<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c1">"واهي الحديث"</span>. <span class="c1">"الفتح"</span> <span class="c2">(١٠/ ٥٤٩)</span>. <span class="c1">"واه"</span>. <span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(٨/ ٢٥١)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c1">"متروك"</span>. <span class="c1">"الفتح"</span> <span class="c2">(١٣/ ٢٢٠، ٥٢٣)</span>، و<span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(٤/ ٥٦٣)</span>، و<span class="c1">"الكشاف"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٧٨)</span>، و<span class="c1">"المطالب"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٣٥٥)</span>، و<span class="c1">"اللسان"</span> <span class="c2">(٣/ ٦٦٩)</span>.<span class="c5"> ترجمة:</span> عباد الهنائي.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
